===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|pĕng'gwĭn, pĕn'gwĭn}}
* {{audio|en-us-penguin.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Any of several [[flightless]] [[sea bird]]s, of [[order]] ''[[Sphenisciformes]]'', found in the [[Southern Hemisphere]]; marked by their usual upright stance, walking on short legs, and (generally) their stark black and white plumage.
# {{slang}} a [[nun]]

